-- GE names new lead independent director
-- By Ankit Ajmera in Bangalore
-- Wed Apr 23, 2014 03:07PM EDT
-- None



April 23 (Reuters) - General Electric Co <GE.N> named John Brennan as its lead independent director, succeeding Ralph Larsen, who retires on Wednesday.

Brennan will also be the chairman of GE's management development and compensation committee, the company said in a filing with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission. [ID:nEOL4rsvdV]